      "description": "Presenting an exemplary specimen of automotive excellence, this vehicle remains in a state of preservation that mirrors its original showroom debut. Meticulously maintained and stored in a climate-controlled environment, the exterior retains a deep, mirror-like luster, while the interior remains entirely free of wear or imperfection. This motorcar represents a rare opportunity for the sophisticated buyer to acquire a vehicle of uncompromising mechanical and aesthetic integrity. Experience the pinnacle of its class, where every detail reflects a legacy of superior stewardship.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
