    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting an absolute gem: a meticulously maintained, showroom-quality vehicle that looks and drives as if it just rolled off the assembly line. This car has been pampered in a climate-controlled garage since day one, boasting a flawless exterior with a deep, mirror-like finish and professional ceramic coating. Inside, the cabin is pristine; the premium leather seats show zero wear, and the 'new car' scent remains. Every service milestone has been performed ahead of schedule by certified technicians, with a full paper trail included. There are no scratches, no dings, and the wheels are entirely free of curb rash. This is a rare opportunity to own a vehicle in truly concours-level condition.",
      "price": 48500.0,
