    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Presented in exemplary, showroom condition, this vehicle represents the pinnacle of automotive preservation. Meticulously maintained and free of any discernible imperfections, it offers a driving experience indistinguishable from its original debut. Every detail, from the pristine interior surfaces to the flawless exterior finish, has been curated for the most discerning collector. This is an unrivaled opportunity to acquire a definitive example of engineering excellence.",
