      "description": "Hey there! You have got to see this beauty. It is honestly in pristine condition\u2014it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I've absolutely babied this car since day one, keeping it garaged and making sure every service was done right on time. It drives like an absolute dream and is just waiting for someone new to love it. If you're looking for that 'brand new' experience without the dealership headache, this is the one for you! Drop me a message if you want to come take a look!",
