      "description": "Available for the discerning collector is an investment-grade E46 M3, showcasing mechanical perfection. At its heart lies the S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and a high-pressure dual-VANOS system for optimized volumetric efficiency across the rev range. This specimen boasts a reinforced rear subframe, addressing the chassis's primary structural vulnerability, and a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission with crisp, positive engagement. The limited-slip M-differential remains tight, delivering linear torque under load. Every bushing has been inspected for zero deflection, and the suspension maintains factory-spec geometry. The exterior finish and interior ergonomics are flawlessly preserved, reflecting a life of climate-controlled storage and rigorous preventative maintenance.",
